SELECT id, 10,
  'expert',
  'Three-Asset Portfolio - Greenville/Oconee County — Three-Asset Specialty Portfolio Capstone (Greenville/Oconee Co.)',
  'You are appraising the property at Three-Asset Portfolio - Greenville/Oconee County, SC (Private consulting capstone - full specialty market synthesis for investment committee presentation · Asset 1: Lake Hartwell (Oconee Co.) / Asset 2: Augusta Road (Greenville) / Asset 3: Lowndes Hill (Greenville)). Private consulting capstone. Client is evaluating a three-asset specialty portfolio: (1) a Lake Hartwell STR cottage; (2) an Augusta Road teardown/redevelopment opportunity; (3) a Greenville ADU property. You must identify all present indicators for each asset, classify correctly, and synthesize a differentiated investment committee recommendation. Section 6 — Market Analysis — requires you to identify which market indicators and external factors are present in the data package, classify each present indicator as Improving, Stable, Declining, or Market-Dependent based on the indicator data and external context, and write a market-supported rationale citing specific data from the indicator table or external context. Indicators not evidenced in the data package must be left unchecked. Every classification must be grounded in specific evidence — this assignment evaluates evidence-based market analysis, not pattern recognition or reflexive checklist behavior.'
FROM scenario_categories WHERE code = 'M2-S6-C6';

